sub_title: Dutch - Polish language teacher at Van Amstel Language School, available for freelance projects
summary:
An experienced and passionate Polish and Dutch language teacher and polyglot, providing diverse language solutions for people of all ages and at all levels. As the owner of the Van Amstel Language school and an experienced private tutor, I’m able to effectively deal with any challenge related to the Polish or Dutch language and culture. Dutch and Polish native speaker. 

Contact me for services related to:
- Dutch and Polish language training for groups and individuals
- Dutch, Polish and English translation services 
- Language training for corporate employees
- Creating educational content for language lessons
- Copywriting in Dutch, Polish and English
- Pools-Nederlandse taalcursussen, taaltraining, coaching voor Poolse medewerkers
